title: [PS3] Valiant Hearts: The Great War
description:
<a href="http://valianthearts.ubi.com/game/en-GB/home/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://valianthearts.ubi.com/game/en-GB/home/</a>


Get your hands on a 2D animated comic book adventure that mixes action and puzzles with exploration.

* Witness the story of crossed destinies and a broken love in a world torn apart.
* Play through the tales of four characters, each trying to survive the horror of the trenches.
* Find historical items, defeat the Baron Von Dorf and save your entire platoon at the battle of the Somme.
